Deck.Flavor_Text: When Titania offered peace, Urza merely turned her down. Mishra made her people pay for the insult.

{T}: Add {B} or {R}.
Deck.Flavor_Text: Swirling eddies of ash hide crumbling cliffs, treacherous drops, and the slavering maws of unknown evils.

Deck.Name: Gnawing Crescendo
Deck.OracleText: Creatures you control get +2/+0 until end of turn. Whenever a nontoken creature you control dies this turn, create a 1/1 black Rat creature token with "This creature can't block."
Deck.Flavor_Text: Totentanz's song had no lyrics, but the rats understood it nonetheless. "You own this land," it said. "You deserve to feast."

Deck.Name: Song of Totentanz
Deck.OracleText: Create X 1/1 black Rat creature tokens with "This creature can't block." Creatures you control gain haste until end of turn.
Deck.Flavor_Text: Townsfolk tapped their feet and hummed along, unwittingly amplifying the tune that would summon their doom.

Deck.Name: Transmogrant's Crown
Deck.Flavor_Text: Fallaji soldiers hated seeing loved ones' faces among the transmogrants. Ashnod devised a solution.

Deck.Name: Tangled Colony

Tangled Colony can't block.
